[[HOW QUAINT->NAP-DREAM-2-1]]<img class="jsExecutionBlock" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" 
onload="
    doPassageLoadMaintenance();
    " />

YOU REMOVE YOUR SUIT'S HELMET

SHAKING YOUR HAIR OUT, WEARING A SMILE

TRYING TO RECALL, FROM A DISTANT PAST LIFE, OR AN IMPOSSIBLE FUTURE, HOW TO BE DESIRABLE

YOU TAKE A STEP FORWARD AND THE BARREL CARESSES YOUR SKIN LIKE A LOVER'S LIPS

YOU CAN SEE CONFUSION IN HER EYES, AND INTEREST, AND WHAT YOU THINK, BUT CANNOT MORALLY BE SURE OF, IS ATTRACTION

[[KISS HER->ASSIGNMENT-2-CUTE-GUARD-CONSENT-FAIL-DEATH]]
[[ASK HER FOR PERMISSION TO KISS HER->ASSIGNMENT-2-CUTE-GUARD-4]]<img class="jsExecutionBlock" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" 
onload="
	window.previousHudVersion = hudVersion;
    $('#hudFaceDiv .censorBar').addClass('visible');
