    	$('#hudFaceDiv .censorBar').removeClass('visible');
    });
	makeHud(0);
    doPassageLoadMaintenance();
    " />

YOU CLOSE YOUR EYES, WET YOUR LIPS, AND LEAN IN

"CONSENT IS NECESSARY TO ERADICATE CISHETEROPATRIARCHAL NORMS!" SHE SHOUTS, AND THE LAST SOUND YOU HEAR IS THE TRIGGER DEPRESSING AND YOUR SKULL TURNING ITSELF [[INSIDE OUT->MEMORY-BAD-DREAMS-1]]<img class="jsExecutionBlock" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" 
