    setCheckpoint();
    " />

"TERRIBLY CLEVER FOR YOU TO SNEAK PAST ALL THE GUARDS LIKE THAT

AND YOU'VE COME TO [[KILL->ASSIGNMENT-1-DATACORE-ENTER-7]] ME"<img class="jsExecutionBlock" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" 
onload="
