YOU ARE BEING TASKED WITH THE DESTRUCTION OF THE SEMILUMINAL PULSE GENERATOR LOCATED WITHIN THE MARE INSULARUM, OWNED AND OPERATED BY COMSENSE

[[YES SIR/MA'AM/UH... UM->ASSIGNMENT-2-LOG-ON]]<img class="jsExecutionBlock" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" 
onload="
	makeHud(window.previousHudVersion);
